Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1426
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 16-31-3-2; IC 36-8-10.5-7.
Synopsis: Training concerning Alzheimer's disease and dementia.
Requires firefighters and persons who are certified or licensed
providers of emergency medical services to complete training on
Alzheimer's disease and dementia.
Effective: January 1, 2026 (retroactive).
Smith H, Bartels
January 8, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Veterans Affairs and Public
Safety.
2026 IN 1426—LS 6809/DI 92

