1 individuals with autism that is certified by the Indiana emergency
2 medical services commission (created under IC 16-31-2-1).
3 (f) This subsection does not apply to volunteer firefighters. After
4 December 31, 2024, in addition to the requirements of subsections (a),
5 (c), (d), and (e), the minimum basic training requirement for full-time
6 firefighters must include training, which may be completed online or
7 by other means of virtual instruction, that addresses the mental health
8 and wellness of firefighters, including:
