29 (2) NFPA 1001.
30 (3) NFPA 1002.
31 (4) NFPA 1003.
32 (5) NFPA 1006.
33 (6) NFPA 1021.
34 (7) NFPA 1031.
35 (8) NFPA 1033.
36 (9) NFPA 1035.
37 (10) NFPA 1041.
38 (11) NFPA 1521.
39 (12) NFPA 1670.
40 SECTION 3. An emergency is declared for this act.
